h4 Any player
p
	| Whenever a player with this ability is the target of a 
	a(href="/abilities/#{Enums.Actions.SLAM}") #{Constants[Enums.Actions.SLAM]} 
	| attempt, they will always 
	a(href="/abilities/#{Enums.Actions.SLAMBACK}") #{Constants[Enums.Actions.SLAMBACK]}
	|, even if the #{Constants[Enums.Actions.SLAM]} came from behind.
ul
	li The player uses their Speed stat to calculate the number of successes.
	li The player gets the same number of dice as the attacking player.
	li No other modifiers are applied to the player's #{Constants[Enums.Actions.SLAMBACK]}.
p
	| A player with this ability who makes a #{Constants[Enums.Actions.SLAM]}
